{"id":567708653,"lang":"cpp","time":"1 month, 2 weeks","timestamp":1633671232,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"12 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/567708653/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Ugly Number II","memory":"7.7 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int nthUglyNumber(int n) {\n        if(n==0)\n            return 0;\n        if(n==1)\n            return 1;\n        vector<int> dp(n);\n        int t2 = 0;\n        int t3 = 0;\n        int t5 = 0;\n        dp[0] = 1;\n        for(int i=1;i<n;i++){\n            dp[i] = min({dp[t2]*2,dp[t3]*3,dp[t5]*5});\n            if(dp[i] == dp[t2]*2) \n                t2++;\n            if(dp[i] == dp[t3]*3) \n                t3++;\n            if(dp[i] == dp[t5]*5) \n                t5++;\n        }\n        return dp[n-1];\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"ugly-number-ii"}
